snippet.title: Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA Mega Mix+ | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA Mega Mix+ debuts on PC, available NOW on Steam! 

🎤 170+ Songs
👗 400+ Costumes
✨ Two Visual Styles
🖌 Custom Playlists & T-shirt Editor
🖼️ Steam Trading Cards
🎵 Get the Extra Song Pack DLC for 72 More Songs

More info here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1761390/

#ProjectDiva #HatsuneMiku
